    <strong>Privacy Policy</strong>

    This Privacy Policy describes how [Your Company Name] ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and discloses your personal information when you use our website [YourWebsite.com] (the "Site") and the services offered through the Site (collectively, the "Services").

    <strong>Information We Collect</strong>

